{"tid":1892230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新撐警藍店-遵理","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:23:19.000Z","uid":217873,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8055a6ae57f572d080053525ad5ed85800b6994","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOPtZRZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOPtZRZ.png&h=0696b9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/obnSG5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FobnSG5t.jpg&h=f1bde20f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現到一個漏洞！大家遺忘咗六月娘！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673817</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n遵理員工遣責暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燈塔老闆六月娘貴為警察榮譽會長，撐警撐到奶鞋底咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前明明po過相 六月之後就del曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知點解遵理幾年前比奧斯卡馬件事搞到上唔到市 ，六月娘都好似唔care？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為條友一早就已經返蝗國搞緊補習同教育，再幫d人落香港考試，做新香港人，大家見到班細路住新界講野歪歪地，有一部分都關佢事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣做同每日150冇咩分別，反而仲恐怖。每日150有好多中年/廢老，過幾年就瓜柴，但係佢送班蝗落黎係搶大家資源同學位，都係製造緊會票投民建聯嘅年輕一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記得，佢手頭上係有極大量呢幾屆應屆dse考生嘅資料，點解拉人可以拉得咁快？咁大個data base .... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講係講到咁多，歡迎補充。學生們，其實燈塔真係垃圾黎，出面大把中小型勁好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（旗下有老師係黃就真嘅，不過同好多公務員係黃嘅一樣道理囉，不過提提大家，大家最愛嘅欣師都係偽黃牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[達哥2.0]yylam始終唔肯屌警+藍扮黃事件[多圖]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nhtRyHX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nhtRyHX</a><br />\n#385 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家係有叫過光復香港，係有骨氣就咪撚再補，又話時代革命，又要一車車去補藍到發紅嘅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出面大把好老師，問下身邊同學，再唔係ig開個po問，毒撚就上校園台問人有咩推薦。<br />\n<br />\n我祝繼續補燈塔嘅你中文攞2，去做毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遵理老闆June Leung擔任黑警會會長，本身同CCTVB、中國移動既關係千絲萬縷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為身有屎自去年六月起就delete咗自己FB 和IG，然後叫前線導師扮黃繼續呃學生錢，比美心集團更可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cd8cbb8faee45ac77a5dae3cb4dc4b528bd1472e","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44995660acd418e127340c3e7839d406590b1bd9","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bfb5fceb5f796de7e82ca5a727611a37fa3430","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e00c5db8254baaa5eac89542be8b1b2b99eb075","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c9148c4e09edcde9e1ce4bceaa60d359d9f89b","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85d11ddf07681b62fe5d6185a0d45a125779b92","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fe8bf0749d8474fb72745890f7328796a71f30","tid":1892230,"uid":301868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"遵理之前搞日校，學界比賽請港隊幫手，但人地已經放棄讀書做冷氣學徒，就叫人唔洗返學，淨係比賽先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b25d98589a71986f41c66d84b15013abafd3b27","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7fe8bf0749d8474fb72745890f7328796a71f30","tid":1892230,"uid":301868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"遵理之前搞日校，學界比賽請港隊幫手，但人地已經放棄讀書做冷氣學徒，就叫人唔洗返學，淨係比賽先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"佢哋一向都好嗱喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係點做黑警會會長？"},{"pid":"7d8ac30e4723f035c526357c4cc08d858260dbf6","tid":1892230,"uid":235630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"都唔新啦 呢間不嬲紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be627981ec1a1ce730251bf2cb5b0da6b4d2b1ee","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d8ac30e4723f035c526357c4cc08d858260dbf6","tid":1892230,"uid":235630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"都唔新啦 呢間不嬲紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"要推爆呢啲撐警藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c907f9a40107d3e27a62f1271be48d6ef2b956fd","tid":1892230,"uid":217873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:40:36.000Z","msg"